  87    def mono_pred_analysis_structure_analysis_next_2(self) -> None:
  88        """Shows the gui elements for the chain selection of protein 1."""
  89        self._view.wait_spinner.start()
  90        tmp_proteins_to_predict: list[str] = []
  91        for i in range(self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_mono_prot_to_predict.rowCount()):
  92            tmp_proteins_to_predict.append(
  93                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_mono_prot_to_predict.verticalHeaderItem(i).text(),
  94            )
  95        self._active_task = tasks.Task(
  96            target=main_presenter_async.check_chains_for_subsequent_analysis,
  97            args=(
  98                self._view.ui.box_pred_analysis_mono_prot_struct_1.currentText(),
  99                self._view.ui.box_pred_analysis_mono_prot_struct_2.currentText(),
 100                self._interface_manager.get_current_project(),
 101                tmp_proteins_to_predict,
 102            ),
 103            post_func=self.__await_mono_pred_analysis_structure_analysis_next_2,
 104        )
 105        self._active_task.start()

 206    def start_monomer_prediction_analysis(self):
 207        tmp_prediction_runs: list[
 208            prediction_protein_info.PredictionProteinInfo
 209        ] = prediction_util.get_prediction_name_and_seq_from_table(
 210            self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_mono_prot_to_predict)
 211        self._view.close()
 212        self.job_input.emit(
 213            ("job_input",
 214             tmp_prediction_runs,
 215             self.prediction_configuration,
 216             True)
 217        )

 219    def check_if_prediction_and_analysis_should_be_done(self):
 220        if self._view.ui.checkbox_add_analysis.isChecked():
 221            self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_mono_go_analysis_setup.setText("Go")
 222            self._view.ui.lbl_pred_analysis_mono_to_analysis_setup.setText("To Analysis Setup")
 223        else:
 224            self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_mono_go_analysis_setup.setText("Predict")
 225            self._view.ui.lbl_pred_analysis_mono_to_analysis_setup.setText("Protein Structure(s)")

 227    def switch_monomer_pred_analysis_tab(self) -> None:
 228        """Switches the tabs from prediction to analysis and vice versa."""
 229        if self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_mono_go_analysis_setup.text() == "Predict":
 230            tmp_prediction_runs: list[
 231                prediction_protein_info.PredictionProteinInfo

 233            self._view.close()

 333    def show_prediction_configuration(self) -> None:
 334        """Opens the prediction configuration dialog window."""
 335        config = dialog_advanced_prediction_configurations.DialogAdvancedPredictionConfigurations(
 336            self.prediction_configuration,
 337        )
 338        config.exec_()
 339        self.prediction_configuration.amber_force_field = config.prediction_config.amber_force_field
 340        self.prediction_configuration.templates = config.prediction_config.templates

 343    def _init_mono_pred_analysis_page(self) -> None:
 344        """Clears all text boxes and sets default values for the gui elements."""
 345        # <editor-fold desc="Prediction section">
 346        self._view.ui.txt_pred_analysis_mono_prot_name.clear()
 347        self._view.ui.txt_pred_analysis_mono_seq_name.clear()
 348        for i in range(self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_mono_prot_to_predict.rowCount()):
 349            self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_mono_prot_to_predict.removeRow(i)
 350        # sets up defaults: Prediction
 351        self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_mono_next.setEnabled(False)
 352        self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_mono_add_protein.setEnabled(False)
 353        self._view.ui.lbl_pred_analysis_mono_prot_name_status.setText("")
 354        self._view.ui.lbl_pred_analysis_mono_seq_name_status.setText("")
 355
 356        # </editor-fold>
 357
 358        # <editor-fold desc="Analysis section">
 359        self._view.ui.list_pred_analysis_mono_overview.clear()
 360        self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_mono_remove.hide()

 364    def display_monomer_pred_analysis(self) -> None:
 365        """Displays the monomer prediction + analysis page."""
 366        self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_mono_go_analysis_setup.setText("Predict")
 367        self._view.ui.lbl_pred_analysis_mono_to_analysis_setup.setText("Protein Structure(s)")
 368        # checks internet connection
 369        if not tools.check_internet_connectivity():
 370            gui_utils.no_internet_dialog()
 371            return
 372
 373        self._init_mono_pred_analysis_page()
 374        self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_mono_prot_to_predict.clear()
 375        self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_mono_prot_to_predict.setHorizontalHeaderItem(
 376            0,

 418    def mono_pred_analysis_validate_protein_name(self) -> None:
 419        """Validates the input of the protein name in real-time."""
 420        if safeguard.Safeguard.check_if_value_is_in_table_v_header(
 421                self._view.ui.txt_pred_analysis_mono_prot_name.text(),
 422                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_mono_prot_to_predict,
 423        ):
 424            self._view.ui.lbl_pred_analysis_mono_prot_name_status.setText("Protein name already used.")
 425            self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_mono_next.setEnabled(False)

 427            self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_mono_next.setEnabled(True)
 428            tools.validate_protein_name(
 429                self._view.ui.txt_pred_analysis_mono_prot_name,
 430                self._view.ui.lbl_pred_analysis_mono_prot_name_status,
 431                self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_mono_next,
 432            )

 421        if safeguard.Safeguard.check_if_value_is_in_table_v_header(
 422                self._view.ui.txt_pred_analysis_mono_prot_name.text(),
 423                self._view.ui.table_pred_analysis_mono_prot_to_predict,

 426            self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_mono_next.setEnabled(False)

 432                self._view.ui.btn_pred_analysis_mono_next,
